<H2>Advanced Menu</H2>
<P>The advanced menu provides options for the more advanced configuration of the packaging
system.</P>
<P>This menu is a sub menu shown from the menu for the iconbar icon</P>
<P>It provides the following options
<UL>
<LI>Sources - shows the <A HREF="sources.htm">Sources Window</A>
    which allows you to select the packaging sites to use.
</LI>
<LI>Paths - shows the <A HREF="paths.htm">Paths Window</A>
    which allows you to specify the base directories the packages are installed to.
</LI>
<LI>Backups - shows the <A HREF="backupwnd.htm">Backups Window</A>
    which allows you to manage application backups made by PackMan.</A>
<LI>Cache - shows the <A HREF="cache.htm">Cache Window</A>
    which allows you to clear the cache of downloaded packages.
</LI>
</UL>
</P>

</BODY>
